  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个教育内容评论的状态流转图，覆盖从创建到最终归档或删除的完整生命周期。核心场景是LMS门户里的评论，经过审核后可能同步到成绩系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Pending",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下结构。评论创建后先进入Pending状态，这个Pending内部是不是还需要细分？比如先进入等待审核的子状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Pending是一个复合状态，内部包含AwaitingModeration。审核通过后流转到Approved，被拒绝则到Rejected，这两个都是终态前的关键分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了Pending内部的AwaitingModeration，以及到Approved和Rejected的分支。Approved这边我打算做成另一个复合状态，包含Visible和Edited的循环，因为已批准的评论可以反复编辑更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Approved的设计可以，但Rejected也需要细化。被拒绝的评论默认Hidden，但运营同事需要填写拒绝原因，所以加个WithReason子状态，填完原因后再同步到成绩系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Rejected内部是Hidden到WithReason的流转。另外我注意到Deleted比较特殊，它从Pending、Approved、Rejected都能直接到达，而且最终都指向GradeSync，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Deleted",
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Deleted是统一出口。还有几个注释需要加上：Pending处说明评论起始待审核，Approved处说明可见且可编辑，Rejected处说明隐藏并可填原因，Deleted处说明永久移除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。四个注释已放在对应状态的右侧，复合状态的层级关系也清晰了。整个流程从LMS门户创建，经过审核分支，最终归档或删除后同步到成绩系统。",
